&lt;p>The programme of seminars focuses on: &lt;/p> 
&lt;ul> 
 &lt;li>Theoretical, empirical and educational perspectives on reading comprehension &lt;/li> 
 &lt;li>Language foundations of reading comprehension &lt;/li> 
 &lt;li>Working memory and text comprehension &lt;/li> 
 &lt;li>Interventions to promote reading comprehension. &lt;/li>
